OL,5, Pop superstar Rihanna will headline the
OL,6, half-time show at February's Super Bowl
OL,7, in Arizona, the NFL has announced.     
OL,9,FThe nine-time Grammy winner broke the  
OL,10,Fnews by posting a photo of an NFL      
OL,11,Fbranded football to Twitter.           
OL,13,FOrganisers called the 34-year-old a    
OL,14,F"generational talent" in a press       
OL,15,Frelease issued on Sunday night.        
OL,17,FThe show is one of the most coveted    
OL,18,Fslots in music, with this year's       
OL,19,F14-minute spectacle drawing in more    
OL,20,Fthan 120 million viewers, the NFL said.
